description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 moving puzzles are included.
-Japanese Garden with Fluttering Cherry Blossoms
-Snow seen from a Japanese-style room
-Cherry blossoms illuminated at night
-Shrine of the Mysterious Rainy Day
-Cherry blossoms at night seen from a Japanese-style room
-Shrine on a bewitching rainy day
-Fantastic snowy scenery
-Fireworks seen from a Japanese-style room
-Row of trees with fluttering cherry blossoms
-Shrine on a rainy night
name: [Moving] Japanese Landscapes by CG
